{"tid":2188920,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【日本Falcom】綜合討論區Vol.59【- 牙軌已死之創之軌跡3 -】","createTime":"2020-09-04T14:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T17:16:05.000Z","uid":18102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"403806a0a4106e3baa9a51897752392686d78b24","tid":2188920,"uid":18102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:01:27.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j7B3nfT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj7B3nfT.gif&h=4467bef6&s={SIZE}\" /></p>"},{"pid":"65e84f4389cf3588508a94569a488f6ded0694e6","tid":2188920,"uid":18102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:02:08.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/24/153412_b1eb08ecb8ac9ec4d76a902cf9e3d486.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F24%2F153412_b1eb08ecb8ac9ec4d76a902cf9e3d486.gif&h=dab1a390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><ins><span class=\"gold\">Falcom 3大柱</span></ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nheGPaB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnheGPaB.png&h=eda3ae17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">軌跡系列</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0N3NrmQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0N3NrmQ.png&h=e50b737a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span class=\"orange\">伊蘇系列</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aLK6taP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaLK6taP.jpg&h=03e923b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><del>幻都</del>404系列</span></p><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"red\">軌跡系列</span></ins><br />\n目前由4篇章 - 10集構成 由零軌開始脫離英雄傳說系列嘅編號<br />\n先後次序由 空軌FC -&gt; SC -&gt; 3rd -&gt; 零軌 -&gt; 碧軌 -&gt; 閃I -&gt; II -&gt; III -&gt; IV -&gt; 創軌<br />\n外加曉/星軌(平行世界) 時間由零碧中間開始  仲有神作 - 羈絆 &amp; OL<br />\n創軌之後仲有1xxx年嘅UNDER INVESTIGATION<br />\n軌跡系列網站<a href=\"https://www.falcom.co.jp/kiseki/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.falcom.co.jp%2Fkiseki%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=9b5e71f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.falcom.co.jp/kiseki/</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"orange\">伊蘇系列</span></ins><br />\n目前共9集 包括伊蘇I - II , 伊蘇III (菲爾佳娜之誓) , 伊蘇IV (塞爾塞塔的樹海) , 伊蘇V (失落的砂之都凱芬) , 伊蘇VI (納比斯汀的方舟) , 伊蘇VII , 伊蘇VIII (丹娜的隕涕日) , 伊蘇 始源<br />\n伊蘇系列除咗I - II外 其他都無實質嘅遊玩次序<br />\n新作 伊蘇Ⅸ -Monstrum NOX- 已於2019年9月推出<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"violet\"><del>幻都</del>404系列</span></ins><br />\n雖然只有5集 但係3大柱之中最歷史悠久 最初同英雄傳說一樣都屬於屠龍者系列<br />\n<del>最新作 東京幻都 社長有意再獨立系列化</del> 垃圾 無人權"},{"pid":"2e40056a41e092fc7781c61f31023cb0a9f3e271","tid":2188920,"uid":18102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"收到風牙軌去左玩東幼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f53e38f0888858858d1efc882b6b2bb0308beea","tid":2188920,"uid":30092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"抄PO<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4602b040c5d14ea1671f1ffa8b97b05e16223bc8","tid":2188920,"uid":18102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f53e38f0888858858d1efc882b6b2bb0308beea","tid":2188920,"uid":30092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"抄PO<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:12:55.000Z","msg":"你又唔開POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721bdb22f68def15cb3c83a826e9ba67fb88b067","tid":2188920,"uid":18102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:13:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2188922/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2188922/page/1</a>"